{"tid":1606442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[制裁] 如何方便美國財政部制裁前線狗","createTime":"2019-09-30T14:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T03:25:05.000Z","uid":326120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cda8356b42fb6f45c6959443a903e86335643990","tid":1606442,"uid":326120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"金融業合規部從業員表示：美國財政部制裁需要以下最少三樣野<br />\n<br />\n1) 英文全名<br />\n2) 出生年月日<br />\n3) 國籍(最好有ID number, 企非mandatory)<br />\n<br />\n就咁得個組織名(eg 香港警隊) 佢係制裁唔到前線d狗，所以麻煩大家(唔知老豆搵仔admin見唔見到) 準備一條list有齊以上三樣野，咁先最有效送到最   多   既狗一程。<br />\n<br />\n一提，我見好多人話制裁d狗等佢地無得去美國旅行/讀書諸如此類，咁樣係便宜佢地。最有力既制裁係美國財政部既制裁，因為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n1) 所有係美國業務既銀行都要exit所有狗account，包括出糧，信用卡同按歇。<br />\n2) 如果前線狗有按歇銀行要即刻call loan，有樓既狗都要跳樓因為唔未必有香港既銀行夠膽呢d受制裁人士既生意，上唔到會就收樓。<br />\n3) 進一步問題係香港既內銀夠唔夠膽接呢d被制裁既狗既生意 - 接既話，成間內銀可能會被美國制裁美元交收能力(視乎美帝係唔係真係認真)，老共可以支爆，唔接既話狗隊就會反政府，因為無糧出，成件事立即昇華。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以，第一步係必須要盡快準備一條制裁名單齊哂以上三樣資料，最好可以名單內每個人都可以附上一條link (影片) 以證明該名被制裁人士係制裁範圍內既人。</strong>"},{"pid":"7496a8b803f27c1301271d68c0ef771e89d39446","tid":1606442,"uid":326120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a073a20627bd2f1e2e017487fcb457e7da751b52","tid":1606442,"uid":326120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b09bfd64ad84e9ef139d30b41a5784f7f720803e","tid":1606442,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b20cfcaf689685aab8b9a8d581e2c9d266a410","tid":1606442,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbfd2e989ea279906d7f6bf8209369648e7e41e","tid":1606442,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkchronicles.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkchronicles.com%2F&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6hZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=1126c166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkchronicles.com/</a>"},{"pid":"4a69ecb1b620b9e18f22175e888ccaca6c6836c6","tid":1606442,"uid":326120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"push"}]}